---
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';
import FallingField from './FallingField.astro';

const games = await getCollection('games');
---

<section class="gm-hero">
  <div class="gm-hero-grid" aria-hidden="true">
    <FallingField />
  </div>
  <div class="gm-hero-inner">
    <div class="gm-eyebrow fp-mono">game.fujioha.com · あそびば</div>
    <h1 class="gm-title">
      <span class="gm-title-jp fp-jp">思いつきの</span>
      <span class="gm-title-en">Web Games</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="gm-lede">
      <span class="fp-jp"
        >ジャンルはばらばら。ブラウザを開けば、その場で遊べる小さなゲームの棚です。だいたい一分で終わります。</span
      >
      <span class="fp-en fp-mute"
        >A shelf of small browser games — different shapes, different rules,
        no installs. Most of them end in about a minute.</span
      >
    </p>
    <div class="gm-hero-meta">
      <span class="gm-chip fp-mono">{games.length} games</span>
      <span class="gm-chip fp-mono">no install · ブラウザで完結</span>
      <span class="gm-chip fp-mono">free</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
